{"word":"H981 - בָּטָא - bâṭâʼ - baw-taw' - Pronounce - உச்சரி","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>בָּטָא"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>bâṭâʼ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>baw-taw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Pronounce / உச்சரி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"பதறிப்பேசு, பேசு - வினைச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to speak rashly or angrily, to speak thoughtlessly"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) one who babbles, one who speaks rashly (participle)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel) to speak rashly or unadvisedly"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>babble</i>; hence to <i>vociferate</i> angrily: - pronounce, speak (unadvisedly)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4008 - מִבְטָא - mibṭâʼ - mib-taw'/4008\">H4008</a>, <a href=\"#/H981 - בָּטָא - bâṭâʼ - baw-taw'/981\">H981</a>"}]}